06:47.074 --> 06:48.850
From the luxury

06:48.950 --> 06:50.852
Of your denial

06:50.952 --> 06:52.854
I press alarms

06:52.954 --> 06:55.732
Place bets on truth

06:55.832 --> 06:59.403
I'm so up and down

